    "IntroductionArtificial intelligence has inevitably become a central part of our lives integrating into our daily lives from being used in Global positioning systems (GPS) to using social media platforms like TikTok, Instagram and Facebook.",
    "AI algorithms are dominating in every field from finance where high-frequency data helps brokers to assess the volatile, unpredictable stock market to medical health care where AI maddress DNA models for cancer research purposes [1].",
    "Moving away from its historically perceived reluctance to adopt technology, the legal industry has made significant strides in integrating artificial intelligence.",
    "This adoption aims to improve procedural efficiency, simplify case management, and increase access to legal services [2].",
    "The legal industry now features an extensive array of AI-enabled tools."
